name: Twin Shadows
plaintext: Summon wraiths to slow and reveal enemy champions
description:
+80 Ability Power
+10% Cooldown Reduction
+6% Movement Speed

UNIQUE Active - Hunt: Summons up to 2 invulnerable ghosts that seek out the 2 nearest enemy champions for 6 seconds. If a ghost reaches its target, it reveals the target and reduces their Movement Speed by 40% for 2.5 seconds.

If a ghost cannot find a target, it tries to return to the caster. Ghosts that successfully return in this way reduce the item's cooldown by 40 seconds (120 second cooldown).
